*opencpn-2.5.0-r1 (02 Dec 2011)

  02 Dec 2011; Marc Schiffbauer <mschiff@gentoo.org> +opencpn-2.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Revbump. USE=gpsd -> USE=gps. Fixes #390973

  19 Nov 2011; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> opencpn-2.5.0.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #390551

  17 Nov 2011; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> opencpn-2.5.0.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #390551

  28 Sep 2011; Marc Schiffbauer <mschiff@gentoo.org> opencpn-2.5.0.ebuild,
  +files/opencpn-2.5.0_tinyxml_stl.patch:
  Add patch to fix linking against tinyxml[stl]. Fixes #384781

*opencpn-2.5.0 (31 Jul 2011)

  31 Jul 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> -opencpn-2.3.1.ebuild,
  +opencpn-2.5.0.ebuild, +files/opencpn-2.5.0-multilib-strict.patch:
  Version bump to latest. Drop older.

  15 Jun 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> opencpn-2.3.1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Add sci-geo as herd. Move gettext only to depend. Rename glu to opengl as the
  goal used to be get rid of glu everywhere.

  15 Jun 2011; Marc Schiffbauer <mschiff@gentoo.org> opencpn-2.3.1.ebuild:
  Drop bogus bzip2 dep and force default build flags

*opencpn-2.3.1 (15 Jun 2011)

  15 Jun 2011; Marc Schiffbauer <mschiff@gentoo.org> +opencpn-2.3.1.ebuild,
  +metadata.xml:
  New ebuild for opencpn. Thanks to Tim Mohlmann for ebuild update. Fixes bug
